    <item>
      <title>纽约市市长称其政策有效控制害虫，纽约市将举办“灭鼠峰会”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/nyc-to-host-rat-summit-as-mayor-says-his-policies-curbed-pests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约市长埃里克·亚当斯表示，他正在赢得灭鼠之战，现在他希望北美其他领导人能够学习他的斗争经验。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/nyc-to-host-rat-summit-as-mayor-says-his-policies-curbed-pests</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 16:26:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普 SPAC 创始人奥兰多赢得媒体公司更多股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/trump-spac-founder-orlando-wins-more-shares-in-media-company</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在联邦监管机构指控他误导投资者两个月后，特拉华州一家法院判定将唐纳德·特朗普社交媒体公司上市的公司前负责人获得了约 80 万股特朗普媒体科技集团公司的股票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/trump-spac-founder-orlando-wins-more-shares-in-media-company</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 16:15:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国官员赴华商谈产能过剩问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/us-officials-head-to-china-for-talks-amid-overcapacity-concerns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周，美国和中国的高级经济官员将在北京举行会谈，拜登政府试图再次向北京表明立场，避免以刺激制造业出口的产业政策激怒世界其他国家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/us-officials-head-to-china-for-talks-amid-overcapacity-concerns</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 15:45:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟选择帮助制定社交媒体规则的技术执行者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/eu-picks-tech-enforcer-who-helped-write-its-social-media-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟提名的新任数字主管是一位资深芬兰议员，她在制定管控大型科技公司的规则方面发挥了核心作用，与她前一天辞职以示抗议、更为张扬的前任形成鲜明对比。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/eu-picks-tech-enforcer-who-helped-write-its-social-media-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 15:42:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟组建团队以避免德拉吉发出“缓慢痛苦”的警告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/eu-builds-team-to-avoid-draghi-s-warning-of-slow-agony-ahead</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌尔苏拉·冯德莱恩宣布了一项雄心勃勃的欧盟委员会重组计划，采纳了前欧洲央行行长马里奥·德拉吉的一些旨在增强欧盟竞争力的建议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/eu-builds-team-to-avoid-draghi-s-warning-of-slow-agony-ahead</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 15:07:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>真主党称以色列策划黎巴嫩境内传呼机爆炸事件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/pagers-in-lebanon-blast-including-hezbollah</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗支持的真主党指责以色列策划了这次袭击，造成黎巴嫩境内数人死亡，近 3,000 人受伤，这加剧了人们对爆发全面战争的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/pagers-in-lebanon-blast-including-hezbollah</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 14:41:21 GMT</pubDate>
